cu.explanation_en: Setting the tracking area code to 0, which is a reserved value, will cause configuration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_msg1_FrequencyStart to 100, which exceeds the valid range, will cause PRACH configuration errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_msg1_FrequencyStart 設定為 100，超過有效範圍，將導致 PRACH 配置錯誤。
